/59-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(64,1,'2014-08-16 21:11:58','2014-08-16 21:11:58','Community\r\n\r\nUnlike other gaming communities, we\'re founded on a basis of support and helping each other. No matter your question, we\'ll be able to help or put you in touch with those who can. See if you can help someone, or sign up to ask your question.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDonate\r\n\r\nYou donations allow us to continue the work of Healing Over Time and in turn benefit charities across the world. From a little to a lot, everything helps.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Get involved','','inherit','open','open','','59-revision-v1','','','2014-08-16 21:11:58','2014-08-16 21:11:58','',59,'http://localhost/2014/08/59-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(65,1,'2014-08-16 21:20:21','2014-08-16 21:20:21','Healing Over Time brings gamers from all walks of life and locations around the world to reach out to those who need a helping hand, no matter where they are.\r\n\r\nWe do this by making it easier for gamers to raise money for their chosen charities and by putting gamers in touch with people, organisations and charities that can benefit them.\r\n<h2>Our Aims</h2>\r\n<h3>Raise the profile of gaming</h3>\r\nThere are people doing good in gaming every day. Be it a chance encounter that helps a new player on their journey, or a large community running a sucessful fundraising event for a good cause, everyone contributes to a positive environment in virtual worlds.\r\n\r\nWe aim to highlight and encourage this positive behaviour, making it easier for gamers to be great citizens.\r\n<h3>Education and support</h3>\r\nJust like any other community, gamers and their families face a wide range of challenges from a variety of sources.\r\n\r\nWe aim to work with other charities and organisations to provide gamers with relevant information and support on a variety of issues, including but not limited to, physical and mental health, conflict resolution, online privacy, harassment, exclusion and accessibility.\r\n<h2>Core beliefs</h2>\r\nTransparency\r\n\r\nEquality\r\n\r\nPassion\r\n<h2>Fundraising</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Organisation Structure</h2>\r\nHealing Over Time is applying to become a non-profit organisation within the United Kingdom. This allows us to minimise our expenditure whilst still being as productive as we possibly can be.\r\n\r\nEveryone supporting the organisation is a volunteer, and all staff members are passionate gamers.','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','23-revision-v1','','','2014-08-16 21:20:21','2014-08-16 21:20:21','',23,'http://localhost/2014/08/23-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(66,1,'2014-08-16 21:22:32','2014-08-16 21:22:32','<script src=\"http://localhost/forum/js/embed.js\"></script>','Community','','inherit','open','open','','22-revision-v1','','','2014-08-16 21:22:32','2014-08-16 21:22:32','',22,'http://localhost/2014/08/22-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(67,1,'2014-08-16 21:22:58','2014-08-16 21:22:58','<a href=\"http://localhost/community\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/lan-697x298.png\" height=\"300\" width=\"700\" data-title=\"Join our community of gamers to see what happens when people come together!\" alt=\"\" class=\"slider-4 slide-44\" /></a>\n<a href=\"http://localhost/community\" target=\"_self\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/5d8d43693f9d24834b86b426a89f28b2-700x300.jpg\" height=\"300\" width=\"700\" data-title=\"Confused guild leader looking for advice? \" alt=\"\" class=\"slider-4 slide-45\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"\" title=\"Error: Sidebar Widgets for Shortcodes with sidebarid widgets_for_shortcodes is empty (no widgets) or is not defined.\">!</a><a href=\"\" title=\"Error: Your requested Widget vanilla discussions is not in the Widgets for Shortcodes sidebar \">!</a><p></p> <a href=\"http://localhost/forum\" >\nJoin our community and become a Healer</a>\n\n<h4>Support</h4>\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"more-button\">More </a>\n\n<h4>Fundraising